Title: GoPro Hero 3 52mm Filter Adapter BlurFix3 Micro 52
Content: Now you can adapt 52 mm filters to your Hero3 camera when using your camera without it's housing! This adapter was made for weight critical applications. You can mount a Neutral Density filter on your Hero3 while flying your quadcopter to minimize or eliminate the "Jello Effect". This adapter is precision CNC machined out of Delrin(R) for ultimate durability....
